---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import imageAbout from "../assets/img/perfil-joseph.webp";
import imageAboutPerfil from "../assets/img/perfil.webp";
---

<section id="sobre" class="relative py-16 xl:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
    <div
      id="parallax-bg"
      class="absolute hidden xl:block inset-0 bg-contain xl:-mt-25 bg-no-repeat opacity-80 scale-110"
      style={`background-image: url(${imageAbout.src}); transition: transform 0.1s ease-out;`}
    >
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-bg/40 via-bg/80 to-bg">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 reveal">
    <div
      class="reveal ml-auto max-w-2xl bg-surface backdrop-blur-xl border border-border rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-14 shadow-2xl"
      style="transition-delay: 0.3s;"
    >
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <span
          class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[2px] mb-2 block"
        >
          Quem sou
        </span>

        {/* Foto Perfil (Mobile) com pulso sutil */}
        <div
          class="lg:hidden w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-primary/50 shadow-lg shadow-primary-glow"
        >
          <Image
            src={imageAboutPerfil}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            alt="Joseph - JR Digital Estudio"
          />
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-white">
          Sobre o Joseph
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Olá! Sou o <span class="text-white font-semibold">Joseph</span>,
          desenvolvedor web de <span class="text-white font-semibold"
            >Belém/PA</span
          >, apaixonado por transformar ideias em sites rápidos, bonitos e que
          realmente convertem.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ajudo empresas e profissionais a terem presença digital sem
          complicação ou custo absurdo.
        </p>
        <p>
          Trabalho com foco em performance, design moderno e atendimento direto
          — você fala comigo do começo ao fim. Vamos construir algo incrível
          juntos?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/5591988649565?text=Olá%20Joseph!%20Vi%20a%20parte%20sobre%20você%20no%20site%20e%20gostaria%20de%20conversar%20sobre%20um%20projeto."
          target="_blank"
          class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-3 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-xl shadow-primary-glow"
        >
          <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-xl"></i>
          Vamos conversar
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
